so_639_1":null,"vote_average":5.844},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/1RKrqGz2TwOEPNMpTMIMnG5kLJk.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":5.616},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/faEI45AK7KlSeFI3ZQs4Iq3Ejjp.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":3.334},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/yg87at336m5vDvmu79pbmlt6giN.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":3.334},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/zkThiZAaAie8Lw7RAc5yPTOewBV.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":2048,"height":1152,"file_path":"/2kOpEq6mYjrDXnTMorGh5342qaW.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/3cZU7saXoZYmE73UKvElwzz7fas.jpg","iso_639_1":"pt","vote_average":3.334},{"width":1840,"height":1035,"file_path":"/nWpL5IeV5z0OCcyIgmLIsADODhE.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":2.278},{"width":2048,"height":1152,"file_path":"/6yC4XcKQmUjRMvEyLszMHuwDnS1.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":2.278},{"width":2000,"height":1123,"file_path":"/19SRdYFaxTbqG8rc9CpXmfLpPoM.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":2.278},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/zbSLWBA82bWnxhNpIY8BP8qPgco.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":2.278},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/uLgDCh5gU7D280kauumxzDglDog.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":2.278},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/eB7TCPGsoc8liVR3SmAxeBYRUgn.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-21T11:41:04.331+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"My Neighbor Totoro","runtime":86,"tagline":"He's your friendly neighbourhood forest spirit!","homepage":"https://gkids.com/films/my-neighbor-totoro","overview":"Two sisters move to the country with their father in order to be closer to their hospitalized mother, and discover the surrounding trees are inhabited by Totoros, magical spirits of the forest. When the youngest runs away from home, the older sister seeks help from the spirits to find her."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Mein Nachbar Totoro","runtime":86,"tagline":"Er ist dein freundlicher Waldgeist aus der Nachbarschaft!","homepage":"","overview":"Die 8-jährige Satsuki und ihre kleine Schwester Mei ziehen mit ihrem Vater, einem Universitätsprofessor, auf das Land. Sie wollen in der Nähe ihrer Mutter sein, die sich in einem nahe gelegenen Krankenhaus von einer schweren Krankheit erholt. Ihr neues Zuhause ist ein altes Bauernhaus, das einige Zeit unbewohnt war. Beim Spielen auf dem Hof entdeckt die kleine Mei eines Tages ein winziges Wesen mit einem Sack, das Eicheln sammelt. Sie folgt ihm in den Wald und klettert durch das Gestrüpp. Plötzlich fällt sie in ein Loch im Stamm eines riesigen Baumes. Am Ende des Loches trifft sie auf den fest schlafenden Totoro, eine riesige fellige Kreatur, die fast so groß ist wie ein kleines Haus. Die Kinder freunden sich schnell mit dem magischen Wesen an und erleben gemeinsam mit ihm viele tolle Abenteuer."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":86,"tagline":"このへんな生きものは、まだ日本にいるのです。たぶん。","homepage":"https://www.ghibli.jp/works/totoro/","overview":"都会からそんなに遠くない田舎町に引っ越してきたサツキとメイ。お化けやしきみたいに古い家には、何かが棲んでいる気配がいっぱい。サツキたちの家の裏にある神社の大木をすみかにしているトトロ。人の住んでいない家をススやホコリだらけにしてしまうススワタリ（まっくろくろすけ）。大きな目と大きな口、そして何本もある足で空間を自由自在に走りまわる巨大なネコバス。サツキとメイは次々に奇妙ないきものと出会い、ステキな冒険に飛び出す。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"Мой сосед Тоторо","runtime":86,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://gkids.com/films/my-neighbor-totoro","overview":"Сестры Сацуки и Мэй переезжают вместе с папой в деревенский дом. Однажды девочки обнаруживают, что по соседству с ними живут лесные духи — хранители леса во главе со своим могущественным и добрым повелителем Тоторо. Постепенно Тоторо становится другом девочек, помогая им в их повседневных приключениях."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Mon voisin Totoro","runtime":87,"tagline":"C'est l'esprit de la forêt de votre quartier!","homepage":"","overview":"Mei, 4 ans, et Satsuki, 10 ans, s’installent à la campagne avec leur père pour se rapprocher de l’hôpital où séjourne leur mère. Elles découvrent la nature tout autour de la maison et, surtout, l’existence d’animaux étranges et merveilleux, les Totoros, avec qui elles deviennent très amies. Un jour, alors que Satsuki et Mei attendent le retour de leur mère, elles apprennent que sa sortie de l’hôpital a été repoussée. Mei décide alors d’aller lui rendre visite seule. Satsuki et les gens du village la recherchent en vain. Désespérée, Satsuki va finalement demander de l’aide à son voisin Totoro."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Mi vecino Totoro","runtime":86,"tagline":"Estas extrañas criaturas aún existen en Japón. Probablemente...","homepage":"","overview":"Dos chicas jóvenes, Mei y Satsuki, se mudan a una nueva casa cerca del hospital en el que se encuentra su madre. En el patio junto a la casa, existe un gran árbol que es el hogar de tres Totoros, dioses de la selva. Poco después, reciben noticias desde el hospital de que su madre no puede venir a casa como había prometido, por lo que Mei (la más joven) se escapa para ir a visitarla. Satsuki tiene que recurrir a un Totoro para ayudar a encontrarla."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"龙猫","runtime":0,"tagline":"让我们去见龙猫吧","homepage":"","overview":"小月的母亲生病住院了，父亲带着她与四岁的妹妹小梅到乡间的居住。她们对那里的环境都感到十分新奇，也发现了很多有趣的事情。她们遇到了很多小精灵，她们来到属于她们的环境中，看到了她们世界中很多的奇怪事物，更与一只大大胖胖的龙猫成为了朋友。龙猫与小精灵们利用他们的神奇力量，为小月与妹妹带来了很多神奇的景观，令她们大开眼界。\r 妹妹小梅常常挂念生病中的母亲，嚷着要姐姐带着她去看母亲，但小月拒绝了。小梅竟然自己前往，不料途中迷路了，小月只好寻找她的龙猫及小精灵朋友们帮助。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Naapurini Totoro","runtime":87,"tagline":"","homepage":"http://www.cinemamondo.fi/naapurini-totoro/","overview":"Totoro on kunnianosoitus luonnonvoimille. Tarina etenee uuteen kotiin ja läheiseen metsään tutustuvien 10- ja 4-vuotiaiden tyttöjen näkökulmasta. Totoro jakaa hyvää mieltä omapäisesti ja mielivaltaisesti. Totoro on kuin säätila, mahdoton ennustaa. Sen mukaan on vain elettävä. Sen viehätysvoimaa ei voi kiertää eikä väistää. Totoro on maailmanlaajuinen ilmiö. Kerrankin elokuva, joka sopii taatusti kaiken ikäisille."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"Il mio vicino Totoro","runtime":86,"tagline":"È il tuo amichevole spirito della foresta di quartiere!","homepage":"https://www.luckyred.it/movie/il-mio-vicino-totoro/","overview":"Le sorelline Satsuki e Mei si trasferiscono insieme al padre in una nuova casa in campagna. Per le due bambine inizia un viaggio alla scoperta di un nuovo mondo, abitato da creature fantastiche: dai nerini del buio, spiritelli della fuliggine, a buffi esseri di pelo di varie dimensioni, tra cui Totoro, lo spirito buono della foresta! Insieme a lui, Satsuki e la piccola Mei vivranno una magica e straordinaria avventura all’insegna dell’amicizia!"},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"O Meu Vizinho Totoro","runtime":86,"tagline":"Essas estranhas criaturas ainda existem no Japão. Provavelmente.","homepage":"","overview":"Quando duas raparigas se mudam para o campo para estarem perto da sua mãe em convalescença, passam por aventuras com os fantásticos espíritos da floresta que vivem ali perto."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Min nabo Totoro","runtime":87,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"De to søstre, Mei og Satsuki, flytter på landet med deres kærlige, men nogle gange også lettere distræte far. Huset er hjemsøgt af små, levende nullermænd, som dog ikke er mere faretruende, end at de forføjer sig bort, så snart det runger af latter i stuerne. Den yngste pige falder ned i et dybt hul i jorden og vækker et af underskovens fabeldyr til live. Sammen med denne vidunderlige, flyvske og vennesæle ’skovvogter’ – Totoro, hedder den – begiver børnene sig ud på de mest fantastiske flyveture gennem og over skovene, bl.a. i en blød, tolvbenet kattebus, hvor dyrets øjne fungerer som billygter. Imens vokser den lille Totoro sig stadigt større, uden at den af den grund holder op med at ligne en forvokset kanin!"},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"Min granne Totoro","runtime":87,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://triart.se/filmer/min-granne-totoro/","overview":"Systrarna Satsuki och Mei har flyttat till landet med sin pappa eftersom deras mamma ligger på ett sjukhus i närheten. När Mei utforskar det nya hemmet upptäcker hon att de delar huset med några märkliga varelser och ännu konstigare grannar. Bland annat en stor lurvig varelse som hon kallar Totoro. Deras möte är början, inte bara på en fantastisk vänskap, utan också på ett av filmhistoriens charmigaste familjeäventyr."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Mój sąsiad Totoro","runtime":86,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Dwie dziewczynki, Mei i Satsuki, wraz z ojcem i zmagającą się z ciężką chorobą mamą przeprowadzają się na wieś, do opuszczonego, nieco tajemniczego domu. Szybko odkrywają, że spokojna sielska okolica przepełniona jest magią. Najpierw siostry spotykają mieszkające w ich domu tajemnicze czarne kulki, później poznają łagodne i życzliwe duchy lasu, a wśród nich niezwykłego Totoro. Kiedy młodsza dziewczynka zaginie, okaże się, jak cenna jest ta przyjaźń..."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Můj soused Totoro","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Satsuke a její malá sestřička Mei se společně s tatínkem stěhují do nového domu na venkově. Jejich maminka je v nemocnici, tatínek má hodně práce, a tak oběma zůstává spousta času na seznamování se s novým domovem. Brzy poznají, že dům a jeho okolí  jsou obývány nejrůznějšími kouzelnými bytostmi. Díky zvědavé Mei narazí na dobráckého lesního ducha Totora, se kterým za krátko zažijí nejedno úžasné dobrodružství."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"Totoro - A varázserdő titka","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Kusakabe úr és lányai, Satsuki és Mei vidékre költözik, egy csodálatos tájra, de nem csak a környék, hanem annak lakói is különlegesek; furcsa teremtmények, házi és erdei szellemek. Közülük a leghatalmasabb Totoro, egy barátságos szőrmók, akivel hamar összebarátkoznak hőseink."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Min nabo Totoro","runtime":87,"tagline":"","homepage":"http://starmedia.no/min-nabo-totoro/","overview":"Når Mei og Satsuki flytter på landet møter de Totoro, skogens vokter. Plutselig blir hverdagen fylt av magiske eventyr sammen med den svære skogsguden! En vakker vårdag kommer en tungt lastet bil kjørende gjennom et fredelig og fargesterkt landskap. I bilen sitter ti år gamle Satsuki, den fireårige lillesøstera hennes, Mei, og faren deres. For de to søstrene er dette starten på et spennende eventyr, og de legger ikke skjul på at de håper det gamle huset de skal flytte inn i er hjemsøkt."},"name":"Bokmål","iso_639_1":"nb","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian Bokmål"},{"data":{"title":"Komşum Totoro","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"İki sevimli kız kardeş olan Satsuke ve Mei, babaları ile birlikte hastanede yatan annelerine daha yakın olabilmek için hastanenin yakınındaki bir köy evine taşınırlar. Yeni evlerine alışmaya çalışırlarken inanılmaz bir gerçeğin farkına varırlar. Evlerinin yakınındaki ormanda Totoro isminde, son derece sevimli ve büyülü yaratıklar yaşamaktadır. Bu sevimli yaratıklarla kısa zamanda arkadaş olan Satsuke ve Mei için şehrin telaşından uzakta yepyeni büyülü bir dünyanın kapıları açılacaktır. Yaz zamanının kaygısızlığı üzerine kurulmuş bir aile filmi olarak tasarlanan Komşum Totoro ile Miyazaki'nin unutulmaz karakterleriyle zenginleştirilmiş hayalgücü ve arkadaşlığın bir masalını yaratıyor. Çocukluğun perimasalı dünyasının ve yokolan kırsal alanların yasını tutuyor..."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"My Neighbor Totoro","runtime":86,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Twee meisjes verhuizen met hun vader naar het platteland om in de buurt te zijn van het verpleegtehuis waar hun moeder ligt. Satsuki en Mei ontdekken dat het nabijgelegen bos bevolkt is door wonderlijke wezens."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"이웃집 토토로","runtime":87,"tagline":"행복이 기적처럼 쏟아진다","homepage":"","overview":"1955년 일본의 아름다운 시골 마을, 상냥하고 의젓한 11살 사츠키와 장난꾸러기에 호기심 많은 4살의 메이 는 사이좋은 자매로 아빠와 함께 도시를 떠나 시골로 이사온다. 자상한 아빠 쿠사카베타츠오는 도쿄에서 대학 연구원이며, 입원 중이지만 따뜻한 미소를 잃지 않는 엄마가 있다. 곧 퇴원하실 엄마를 공기가 맑은 곳에서 맞이하기 위해서다. 숲 한복판에 금방이라도 쓰러질 것처럼 낡은 집을 보며 자매는 새로운 환경에 대한 호기심으로 잔뜩 들뜬다. 그러던 어느 날 사츠키가 학교에 간 동안 메이는 숲에서 정령을 만나다. 메이는 그 정령에게 토토로란 이름을 붙여주는데..."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Η Γειτονιά του Δάσους: Οι Περιπέτειες του Τοτόρο","runtime":86,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Δύο αδελφές με τον πατέρα τους, μετακομίζουν στην εξοχή για να είναι πλησιέστερα στο νοσοκομείο που νοσηλεύεται η μητέρα τους. Εκεί θα ανακαλύψουν ότι τα δέντρα της περιοχής κατοικούνται από τους Τότορος, μαγικά πνεύματα του δάσους. Όταν η νεότερη από τις δύο το σκάσει από το σπίτι, η αδελφή της αναζητά βοήθεια από τα πνεύματα για να την βρει."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"השכן הקסום שלי טוטורו","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"שתי האחיות סאצוקי ומיי עוברות עם אביהם לבית בכפר כדי להיות קרובים לאמן המאושפזת בבית חולים קרוב, בגלל מחלה לא ברורה. ביער הסמוך לכפר מתוודעות האחיות לשדון יער בשם טוטורו, המכיר להן עולם שלם של יצורים פרוותים,מצחיקים וקסומים,בינהם גם חתול ענק שמשמש כאוטובוס. כאשר מיי מגלה כי מצבה של אמה מחמיר היא נעלמת, סאצוקי יוצאת למסע חיפושים אחרי מיי, אבל רק טוטורו יכול לסייע לה למצוא אותה."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Мій сусід Тоторо","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Дві сестри переїжджають разом із батьком на літо до японського села. Там вони заводять дружбу із чарівними істотами, що мешкають у лісі неподалік."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"Min nabo Totoro","runtime":87,"tagline":"","homepage":"http://starmedia.no/min-nabo-totoro/","overview":"Når Mei og Satsuki flytter på landet møter de Totoro, skogens vokter. Plutselig blir hverdagen fylt av magiske eventyr sammen med den svære skogsguden! En vakker vårdag kommer en tungt lastet bil kjørende gjennom et fredelig og fargesterkt landskap. I bilen sitter ti år gamle Satsuki, den fireårige lillesøstera hennes, Mei, og faren deres. For de to søstrene er dette starten på et spennende eventyr, og de legger ikke skjul på at de håper det gamle huset de skal flytte inn i er hjemsøkt."},"name":"Norsk","iso_639_1":"no","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian"},{"data":{"title":"Моят съсед Тоторо","runtime":86,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Koгaтo двe мoмичeнцa ce пpeмecтвaт зaeднo c бaщa cи в пpoвинциятa, зa дa бъдaт пo-близĸo дo бoлeдyвaщaтa cи мaйĸa, тe oтĸpивaт, чe в близĸaтa гopичĸa живeят мaгичecĸи гopcĸи cъщecтвa, ĸoитo ce нapичaт „Toтopo“.  Cĸopo тe ce cпpиятeлявaт c тeзи cъщecтвa и пpeживявaт c тяx вълшeбни пpиĸлючeния.  Eднa ĸpacивa пpиĸaзĸa зa дeтcтвoтo и чиcтoтaтa нa дeтcĸaтa дyшa."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"Meu Amigo Totoro","runtime":87,"tagline":"Essas estranhas criaturas ainda existem no Japão. Provavelmente.","homepage":"https://studioghibli.com.br/filmografia/meu-amigo-totoro/","overview":"Duas irmãs se mudam para o campo com o pai para ficarem mais próximas da mãe hospitalizada e descobrem que as árvores ao redor são habitadas por Totoros, espíritos mágicos da floresta. Quando a mais nova foge de casa, a irmã mais velha busca a ajuda dos espíritos para encontrá-la."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"龍貓","runtime":86,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"小月、小梅兩姊妹跟著爸爸一起搬到郊外居住，準備迎接即將出院的母親，那個被戲稱「鬼屋」的新家發生許多神奇的事，包含會突然四散逃走的灰塵精靈，以及神祕的龍貓與貓巴士。有一天，小梅在與姊姊小月吵架後失蹤了，小月只能尋求龍貓的幫助，展開一場尋找妹妹的奇幻冒險…"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"El meu veí Totoro","runtime":0,"tagline":"Aquestes estranyes criatures encara existeixen al Japó. Probablement...","homepage":"","overview":"Relata la història d'una família japonesa que es trasllada al camp als anys 50. Les dues filles, la Satsuki i la Mei, ensopeguen amb un esperit del bosc, Totoro, amb el qual entaulen amistat. El pare és un professor universitari que aviva la imaginació de les filles amb faules i històries màgiques sobre follets, fantasmes i esperits protectors de les llars, mentre la mare es troba malalta a l'hospital. Un dia, la Satsuki rep un telegrama i..."},"name":"Català","iso_639_1":"ca","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Catalan"},{"data":{"title":"Мој комшија Тоторо","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Отац и његове две млађе кћерке, Сатсуки и Меи, преселили су се у нову кућу негде у природи како би били близу њихове мајке која болује од туберколозе у локалној болници. Нова кућа изгледа нормално, али девојчице су у њој приметиле необична мала бића налик на пауке. Касније откривају још необичније биће у шуми, дивовско мачколико створење које назову Тоторо. То испричају свом оцу који им све поверује. Девојчице се спријатеље са Тотором који их повезе у аутобусу налик на мачку. Када је посета болници отказана Меи одлучи сама да оде тамо, али нестане, па се Сатсуки и отац уплаше и крену у потрагу. Опет се појављује Тоторо који поможе Сатсуки да пронађе Меи, те их одводи до болнице где се лечи њихова мајка."},"name":"Srpski","iso_639_1":"sr","iso_3166_1":"RS","english_name":"Serbian"},{"data":{"title":"Môj Sused Totoro","runtime":86,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Osemročná Satsuki a jej malá sestra Mei sa spolu s otcom presťahovali na vidiek. Ich vážne chorá mama je hospitalizovaná v blízkej nemocnici. Starý, zanedbaný dom, v ktorom už dlho nikto nebýval sa stal ich novým domovom. Dievčatá sa okamžite pustia do upratovania a zveľaďovania. Jedného dňa počas hrania sa dvore pred domom zazrie malá Mei malinkú bytosť, ktorá nesie vrecúško so žaluďmi. Nasleduje ju do lesa, kde stretáva Totora, obrovskú chlpatú potvoru veľkú ako malý dom..."},"name":"Slovenčina","iso_639_1":"sk","iso_3166_1":"SK","english_name":"Slovak"},{"data":{"title":"Mia najbaro Totoro","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Japanio, la 50-aj jaroj de pasinta jarcento. La 11-jaraĝa knabino Sacuki, kune kun sia 4-jara fratino Mej kaj ilia patro translokiĝas al domo en la kamparo. La du knabinoj kutimiĝas al nova ĉirkaŭaĵo dume malkvietante pri ilia patrino kiu ankoraŭ troviĝas en hospitalo. La filmo rakontas delikatsente la adventurojn de la du knabinoj amikiĝante al arbaraj spiritoj kiuj vivas en grandega arbo en la najbareco. Kelkaj el ili estas grandaj, aliaj estas malgrandaj. Sed vidi ilin povas nur infanoj, kiujn spiritoj ŝatas."},"name":"Esperanto","iso_639_1":"eo","iso_3166_1":"EO","english_name":"Esperanto"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":86,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Dua orang perempuan kakak beradik pindah ke desa dengan ayah mereka untuk dekat dengan ibu mereka yang sedang dirawat dan menemukan bahwa pepohonan disekitar dihuni oleh para Totoro, jiwa-jiwa magis dari hutan. Ketika saudara termuda mereka melarikan diri dari rumah, saudara perempuan yang lebih tua mencari pertolongan dari jiwa-jiwa magis untuk menemukannya."},"name":"Bahasa indonesia","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","english_name":"Indonesian"},{"data":{"title":"Mi vecino Totoro","runtime":86,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Dos chicas jóvenes, Mei y Satsuki, se mudan a una nueva casa cerca del hospital en el que se encuentra su madre. En el patio junto a la casa ,existe un gran árbol que es el hogar de tres Totoros, dioses de la selva. Poco después, reciben noticias desde el hospital de que su madre no puede venir a casa como había prometido, por lo que Mei (la más joven) se escapa para ir a visitarla. Satsuki tiene que recurrir a un Totoro para ayudar a encontrarla."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"همسایه من، توتورو","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"دو دختربچه به همراه پدرشان به خانه‌ای در دهکده نقل مکان می‌کنند تا به مادر بیمارشان نزدیک‌تر باشند. آن‌ها در جنگل‌های نزدیک دهکده موجوداتی سحر آمیز بنام «تو تو رو» را پیدا می‌کنند و خیلی زود با آن‌ها دوست می‌شوند."},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"Moj susjed Totoro","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Hrvatski","iso_639_1":"hr","iso_3166_1":"HR","english_name":"Croatian"},{"data":{"title":"龍貓","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"本片是對日本鄉村生活的迷人及節奏緩慢的描繪。故事背景設定於1958年（昭和33年），一位大學教授「草壁達郎」（草壁タツオ）和他的兩個女兒「皋月、梅」（サツキ、メイ）搬進一個森林附近的一所舊房子，而教授的妻子「草壁靖子」因染上了結核病，在附近的一所醫院康復中。  搬來新家的皋月和梅，都在家中及附近發現各種奇妙的東西，如家裡藏著像是小黑球模樣的「煤炭球」（ススワタリ）。而梅某一天也在外頭發現可以將外表變不見「小龍貓」（チビトト）、為了追趕它而被引領到樹洞裡發現森林的守護者「大龍貓」（トトロ）；並且在一個下雨的晚上，當皋月和梅在公車站牌邊等爸爸時，她們都遇到了用樹葉擋雨、先前梅在樹洞裡看到的大龍貓。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Vecinul meu Totoro","runtime":86,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Fiți gata să porniți într-o lume fantezistă, colorată, unde numai cei cu suflete de copil îl vor putea întâlni pe Spiritul Pădurii, Totoro! Mei și Sazuki, două surori, trebuie să se mute împreună cu tatăl lor în ceea ce pare a fi o casă bântuită. Entuziasmate de noua casă, pline de credința în basme și cu un suflet bun, cele două îl întâlnesc curând pe Spiritul Pădurii și află că nu toate spiritele sunt înfricoșătoare. Trebuie doar să ai mereu un zâmbet pe față, să râzi cât de tare poți, iar ele te vor invita în lumea lor! Sunteți pregătiți?"},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"جاري توتورو","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"عند احتجاز والدتهما بالمستشفى، أمضت الأختان الصغيرتان الصيف في الريف الياباني بصحبة والدهما."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"โทโทโร่เพื่อนรัก","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ระหว่างใช้เวลาช่วงหน้าร้อนกับพ่อในแถบชนบทของญี่ปุ่น เด็กน้อยสองพี่น้องได้มีโอกาสเป็นเพื่อนกับสิ่งมีชีวิตสุดอัศจรรย์ที่อาศัยอยู่ในป่าใกล้เคียง"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"माय नेबर टोटोरो","runtime":86,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"दो बहनें अपने पिता के साथ अपने अस्पताल में भर्ती होने के लिए अपने पिता के साथ देश जाती हैं, और आसपास के पेड़ों को खोजती हैं, जो जंगल की जादुई आत्माओं में टोटोरोस द्वारा बसा हुआ है। जब सबसे छोटा घर से भाग जाता है, तो बड़ी बहन उसे खोजने के लिए आत्माओं की मदद लेती है।"},"name":"हिन्दी","iso_639_1":"hi","iso_3166_1":"IN","english_name":"Hindi"},{"data":{"title":"Totoro Auzokidea","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Familia batek auzoz aldatu egiten da eta alabek, basoan barrena totoro deituriko basa-katu erraldoi bat ezagutuko dute. Haien abentura ikaragarriak gozatuko dute barre algaraz beteta."},"name":"euskera","iso_639_1":"eu","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Basque"},{"data":{"title":"Minu naaber Totoro","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Film jutustab kahest õest, kes asuvad koos isaga elama maale, et olla lähemal haiglaravil viibivale emale. Uue koduga harjumise juurde käib ka selle ümbruskonna avastamine ja nii satub noorem õde ühe päeval nägema salapäraseid olendeid - Totorosid. Tasahilju saavad tüdrukud nendega sõbraks ja koos satuvad nad seiklustele ning õpivad tundma maagilist vaimudemaailma, kus saab sõita Kassibussiga ja lennata metsade kohal."},"name":"Eesti","iso_639_1":"et","iso_3166_1":"EE","english_name":"Estonian"},{"data":{"title":"Hàng Xóm Của Tôi Là Totoro","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Những ngày cùng cha nghỉ hè tại miền quê thuộc đất nước Nhật Bản, hai chị em bé nhỏ đã kết bạn với những sinh vật huyền bí sống trong khu rừng gần đó."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Мой сусед Тотара","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Маленькая дзяўчынка Мэй, якая зусім нядаўна перабралася са сваёй сям’ёй у новую хату, часта гуляе па навакольных лясах. Падчас аднаго з такіх шпацыраў яна сустракае лясного духа Тотара, які роюбіцца сапраўдным сябрам для маленькай Мэй."},"name":"беларуская мова","iso_639_1":"be","iso_3166_1":"BY","english_name":"Belarusian"},{"data":{"title":"Mano kaimynas Totoro","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Japonija, praeito amžiaus 50-ieji metai. Dvi jaunos mergaitės Satsuki ir Mei, kartu su savo tėvu, persikrausto į namą kaime, kad būtų arčiau savo sergančios ir netoliese besigydančios mamos. Šalia namo yra stebuklingas miškas, kur gyvena keistos būtybės. Kartą nutinka netikėtas dalykas, dėl kurio seserys susipyksta ir išsiskiria..."},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"},{"data":{"title":"ჩემი მეზობელი ტოტორო","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"იაპონია, გასული საუკუნის 50-იანი წლები. ორი პატარა და - საცუკი და მეი სოფელში გადადიან საცხოვრებლად. გოგონები ტყეში საოცარ სამყაროს აღმოაჩენენ, რომელიც არაჩვეულებრივი ფუმფულა არსებებით - ტოტოროებითაა დასახლებული. ისინი მათ მალევე დაუმეგობრდებიან. ზოგი მათგანი ვებერთელაა, ზოგიც მინიატურული, მაგრამ ყველას აქვს კეთილი გული და მაგიური ძალა."},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"},{"data":{"title":"Mon voisin Totoro","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Venues habiter à la campagne avec leur mère malade, deux fillettes vivent de multiples aventures aux côtés des esprits merveilleux de la forêt voisine."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"AT","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Mans kaimiņš Totoro","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Latviešu","iso_639_1":"lv","iso_3166_1":"LV","english_name":"Latvian"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"5ec0827ed2147c0022b1f551","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/5ec0827ed2147c0022b1f551","author":"sykobanana","content":"**\"Childhood\" in a movie.** \r\n\r\nThis is just perfection - a perfect way to while away time and reconnect with your youth.  \r\nEverything is outstanding in this film, but especially the way it can emote your sense of wonder and imagination.\r\n\r\nI wish I could have watched this as a child, I would have wanted to find Totoro and the Catbus, roar like Totoro, or sleep on his belly.  Oh well...I will just have to imagine it.\r\n\r\nIts interesting to note this was released with Grave of the Fireflies, another Ghibli masterpiece, which I have summed up as being about innocence lost.  **This movie is innocence maintained.**","created_at":"2020-05-17T00:17:02.058Z","updated_at":"2021-06-23T15:58:38.132Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":9,"username":"sykobanana","avatar_path":"/j2KpvD880J95lqf3ct4u1MmWZhE.jpg"}},{"id":"5f153a6e78570e00325c4b1b","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/5f153a6e78570e00325c4b1b","author":"20thCentury","content":"$11","created_at":"2020-07-20T06:32:14.183Z","updated_at":"2021-06-23T15:58:40.948Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":null,"username":"20thCentury","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"65b5058358efd3017cca6daa","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/65b5058358efd3017cca6daa","author":"r96sk","content":"Aggressively cute.\r\n\r\n<em>'My Neighbor Totoro'</em> holds an extremely hearty story, one told via impeccably beautiful animation. Noriko Hidaka and Chika Sakamoto standout as Satsuki and Mei, the relationship between those two characters is so sweet. They do get a bit shouty in parts which ever so slightly irritates, but that's definitely one to file under 'nit-picking'.\r\n\r\nA simple movie, one which displays the imagination of children perfectly. Big fan of the Catbus. 🐱","created_at":"2024-01-27T13:30:43.083Z","updated_at":"2024-01-27T13:30:43.214Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":8,"username":"r96sk","avatar_path":"/mwR7rFHoDcobAx1i61I3skzMW3U.jpg"}},{"id":"65e603389979d2017cb5017c","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/65e603389979d2017cb5017c","author":"ARGMAN","content":"cute & sweet. that's it","created_at":"2024-03-04T17:22:00.682Z","updated_at":"2024-03-04T17:22:00.769Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":6,"username":"ARGMAN","avatar_path":"/vS2hgxwL3Dcfmf8ZRWlJ6Xp142Y.jpg"}},{"id":"66b79b5ff2814888220180ee","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/66b79b5ff2814888220180ee","author":"CinemaSerf","content":"$12","created_at":"2024-08-10T16:54:55.359Z","updated_at":"2024-08-10T16:54:55.803Z","author_details":{"name":"CinemaSerf","rating":7,"username":"Geronimo1967","avatar_path":"/9HcQx0Yfbxy8eqr3ft66X9uWMf0.jpg"}}],"recommendations":[{"id":16859,"adult":false,"title":"Kiki's Delivery Service","video":false,"overview":"A young witch, on her mandatory year of independent life, finds fitting into a new community difficult while she supports herself by running an air courier service.","genre_ids":[16,10751,14,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.6261,"vote_count":4459,"poster_path":"/Aufa4YdZIv4AXpR9rznwVA5SEfd.jpg","release_date":"1989-07-29","vote_average":7.83,"backdrop_path":"/h5pAEVma835u8xoE60kmLVopLct.jpg","original_title":"魔女の宅急便","original_language":"ja"},{"id":10515,"adult":false,"title":"Castle in the Sky","video":false,"overview":"A young boy and a girl with a magic crystal must race against pirates and foreign agents in a search for a legendary floating castle.","genre_ids":[12,14,16,28,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.5401,"vote_count":4582,"poster_path":"/41XxSsJc5OrulP0m7TrrUeO2hoz.jpg","release_date":"1986-08-02","vote_average":8,"backdrop_path":"/j2ZvLJyz163MlmBFsoaDYOwxgws.jpg","original_title":"天空の城ラピュタ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":12429,"adult":false,"title":"Ponyo","video":false,"overview":"When Sosuke, a young boy who lives on a clifftop overlooking the sea, rescues a stranded goldfish named Ponyo, he discovers more than he bargained for. Ponyo is a curious, energetic young creature who yearns to be human, but even as she causes chaos around the house, her father, a powerful sorcerer, schemes to return Ponyo to the sea.","genre_ids":[16,14,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.242,"vote_count":4708,"poster_path":"/yp8vEZflGynlEylxEesbYasc06i.jpg","release_date":"2008-07-19","vote_average":7.757,"backdrop_path":"/shqLeIkqPAAXM8iT6wVDiXUYz1p.jpg","original_title":"崖の上のポニョ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":81,"adult":false,"title":"Nausicaä of the Valley of the Wind","video":false,"overview":"After a global war, the seaside kingdom known as the Valley of the Wind remains one of the last strongholds on Earth untouched by a poisonous jungle and the powerful insects that guard it. Led by the courageous Princess Nausicaä, the people of the Valley engage in an epic struggle to restore the bond between humanity and Earth.","genre_ids":[12,16,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.4129,"vote_count":3977,"poster_path":"/tcrkfB8SRPQCgwI88hQScua6nxh.jpg","release_date":"1984-03-11","vote_average":7.948,"backdrop_path":"/ulVUa2MvnJAjAeRt7h23FFJVRKH.jpg","original_title":"風の谷のナウシカ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":4935,"adult":false,"title":"Howl's Moving Castle","video":false,"overview":"Sophie, a young milliner, is turned into an elderly woman by a witch who enters her shop and curses her. She encounters a wizard named Howl and gets caught up in his resistance to fighting for the king.","genre_ids":[14,16,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":13.9617,"vote_count":10832,"poster_path":"/13kOl2v0nD2OLbVSHnHk8GUFEhO.jpg","release_date":"2004-09-09","vote_average":8.387,"backdrop_path":"/pjy0T63vIFYvxRSJ3ZtjB4tmWV4.jpg","original_title":"ハウルの動く城","original_language":"ja"},{"id":128,"adult":false,"title":"Princess Mononoke","video":false,"overview":"Ashitaka, a prince of the disappearing Emishi people, is cursed by a demonized boar god and must journey to the west to find a cure. Along the way, he encounters San, a young human woman fighting to protect the forest, and Lady Eboshi, who is trying to destroy it. Ashitaka must find a way to bring balance to this conflict.","genre_ids":[12,14,16],"media_type":"movie","popularity":10.3567,"vote_count":8776,"poster_path":"/cMYCDADoLKLbB83g4WnJegaZimC.jpg","release_date":"1997-07-12","vote_average":8.323,"backdrop_path":"/gl0jzn4BupSbL2qMVeqrjKkF9Js.jpg","original_title":"もののけ姫","original_language":"ja"},{"id":129,"adult":false,"title":"Spirited Away","video":false,"overview":"A young girl, Chihiro, becomes trapped in a strange new world of spirits. When her parents undergo a mysterious transformation, she must call upon the courage she never knew she had to free her family.","genre_ids":[16,10751,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":18.1524,"vote_count":17970,"poster_path":"/39wmItIWsg5sZMyRUHLkWBcuVCM.jpg","release_date":"2001-07-20","vote_average":8.534,"backdrop_path":"/ukfI9QkU1aIhOhKXYWE9n3z1mFR.jpg","original_title":"千と千尋の神隠し","original_language":"ja"},{"id":12477,"adult":false,"title":"Grave of the Fireflies","video":false,"overview":"In the final months of World War II, 14-year-old Seita and his sister Setsuko are orphaned when their mother is killed during an air raid in Kobe, Japan. After a falling out with their aunt, they move into an abandoned bomb shelter. With no surviving relatives and their emergency rations depleted, Seita and Setsuko struggle to survive.","genre_ids":[16,18,10752],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.0087,"vote_count":6364,"poster_path":"/k9tv1rXZbOhH7eiCk378x61kNQ1.jpg","release_date":"1988-04-16","vote_average":8.443,"backdrop_path":"/aHaqZpOL7UyVu0nKqp3SMz0o2E1.jpg","original_title":"火垂るの墓","original_language":"ja"},{"id":11621,"adult":false,"title":"Porco Rosso","video":false,"overview":"In Italy in the 1930s, sky pirates in biplanes terrorize wealthy cruise ships as they sail the Adriatic Sea. The only pilot brave enough to stop the scourge is the mysterious Porco Rosso, a former World War I flying ace who was somehow turned into a pig during the war. As he prepares to battle the pirate crew's American ace, Porco Rosso enlists the help of spunky girl mechanic Fio Piccolo and his longtime friend Madame Gina.","genre_ids":[10751,35,16,12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.3099,"vote_count":3626,"poster_path":"/8mIvSvnVBApfORL9N6S38Q7wD6A.jpg","release_date":"1992-07-18","vote_average":7.794,"backdrop_path":"/hnpNzxZRC9UHbk73c16XC1qEdEc.jpg","original_title":"紅の豚","original_language":"ja"},{"id":165,"adult":false,"title":"Back to the Future Part II","video":false,"overview":"Marty and Doc are at it again as the time-traveling duo head to 2015 to nip some McFly family woes in the bud. But things go awry thanks to bully Biff Tannen and a pesky sports almanac. In a last-ditch attempt to set things straight, Marty finds himself bound for 1955 and face to face with his teenage parents -- again.","genre_ids":[12,35,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.1854,"vote_count":13683,"poster_path":"/YBawEsTkUZBDajKbd5LiHkmMGf.jpg","release_date":"1989-11-22","vote_average":7.775,"backdrop_path":"/w6tPctxWAsHoQXeKxxNOT6lYKpx.jpg","original_title":"Back to the Future Part II","original_language":"en"},{"id":10360,"adult":false,"title":"Hunger","video":false,"overview":"The story of Bobby Sands, the IRA member who led the 1981 hunger strike during The Troubles in which Irish Republican prisoners tried to win political status.","genre_ids":[18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.5513,"vote_count":1181,"poster_path":"/84HdTM39G2MzyTl8N9R0wVU9I5b.jpg","release_date":"2008-05-15","vote_average":7.242,"backdrop_path":"/34N9iKlR8FdXiu8r8pSpKcyFUVh.jpg","original_title":"Hunger","original_language":"en"},{"id":51739,"adult":false,"title":"The Secret World of Arrietty","video":false,"overview":"14-year-old Arrietty and the rest of the Clock family live in peaceful anonymity as they make their own home from items \"borrowed\" from the house's human inhabitants. However, life changes for the Clocks when a human boy discovers Arrietty.","genre_ids":[14,16,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.8612,"vote_count":3088,"poster_path":"/3lSRaSjDp2nkXMQkzzjpRi3035O.jpg","release_date":"2010-07-16","vote_average":7.666,"backdrop_path":"/7Z7WVzJsSReG8B0CaPk0bvWD7tK.jpg","original_title":"借りぐらしのアリエッティ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":149870,"adult":false,"title":"The Wind Rises","video":false,"overview":"A lifelong love of flight inspires Japanese aviation engineer Jiro Horikoshi, whose storied career includes the creation of the A-6M World War II fighter plane.","genre_ids":[18,16,10749,10752,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.816,"vote_count":3288,"poster_path":"/jfwSexzlIzaOgxP9A8bTA6t8YYb.jpg","release_date":"2013-07-20","vote_average":7.8,"backdrop_path":"/938lqhAQaO3hmLg44VbUR7OqlMs.jpg","original_title":"風立ちぬ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":9003,"adult":false,"title":"Hellraiser","video":false,"overview":"A hedonistic man finds a mysterious puzzle box that summons a group of gruesome beings known as the Cenobites. These otherworldly entities open the doors to a dominion where pain and pleasure are indivisible.","genre_ids":[27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.5717,"vote_count":2802,"poster_path":"/3Z0oPHyLnk3Vx6ZMC1MiVwIrKhO.jpg","release_date":"1987-09-11","vote_average":6.877,"backdrop_path":"/j4irvwRLITgGr6vcP8NIKCUA67y.jpg","original_title":"Hellraiser","original_language":"en"},{"id":40805,"adult":false,"title":"The Green Hornet","video":false,"overview":"Britt Reid, the heir to the largest newspaper fortune in Los Angeles, is a spoiled playboy who has been, thus far, happy to lead an aimless life. After his father dies, Britt meets Kato, a resourceful company employee. Realizing that they have the talent and resources to make something of their lives, Britt and Kato join forces as costumed crime-fighters to bring down the city's most-powerful criminal, Chudnofsky.","genre_ids":[28,80,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.4415,"vote_count":3415,"poster_path":"/1YrRviphr3eXPus9iHyQX56QgIE.jpg","release_date":"2011-01-12","vote_average":5.594,"backdrop_path":"/aBCn1z1tJGivVhY1nHSrXOQqQwG.jpg","original_title":"The Green Hornet","original_language":"en"},{"id":21057,"adult":false,"title":"Ocean Waves","video":false,"overview":"At Kichijōji Station, Tokyo, Taku Morisaki glimpses a familiar woman on the platform opposite boarding a train. Later, her photo falls from a shelf as he exits his apartment before flying to Kōchi Prefecture. Picking it up, he looks at it briefly before leaving. As the aeroplane takes off, he narrates the events that brought her into his life...","genre_ids":[16,18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.2372,"vote_count":951,"poster_path":"/fSR1LLMIJZ6WcQEkM82yKy4F9vQ.jpg","release_date":"1993-10-09","vote_average":6.42,"backdrop_path":"/6ryHAHtpcNTExUVekeaNe0xmDbb.jpg","original_title":"海がきこえる","original_language":"ja"},{"id":15370,"adult":false,"title":"The Cat Returns","video":false,"overview":"Young Haru rescues a cat from being run over, but soon learns it's no ordinary feline; it happens to be the Prince of the Cats.","genre_ids":[12,14,16,18,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.7361,"vote_count":2400,"poster_path":"/pqyY7IEWkCWNZ7EuRStQaJITEta.jpg","release_date":"2002-07-19","vote_average":7.132,"backdrop_path":"/tlQtvjwwTAAbNbtZ7IIGPlY50Hx.jpg","original_title":"猫の恩返し","original_language":"ja"},{"id":37797,"adult":false,"title":"Whisper of the Heart","video":false,"overview":"Shizuku lives a simple life, dominated by her love for stories and writing. One day she notices that all the library books she has have been previously checked out by the same person: 'Seiji Amasawa'.","genre_ids":[16,18,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.4996,"vote_count":2221,"poster_path":"/5FROLD8zpWFs9ja7aYho1uOMJHg.jpg","release_date":"1995-07-15","vote_average":7.95,"backdrop_path":"/rphor0XQcYO4CQoQ6auaQm3UPap.jpg","original_title":"耳をすませば","original_language":"ja"},{"id":15080,"adult":false,"title":"Only Yesterday","video":false,"overview":"In lyrical switches between the present and the past, Taeko contemplates the arc of her life, and wonders if she has been true to the dreams of her childhood self.","genre_ids":[16,18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.5521,"vote_count":1212,"poster_path":"/tOSnFE9e82iH3ZAzSTtuOkBsabJ.jpg","release_date":"1991-07-20","vote_average":7.38,"backdrop_path":"/miA2ALg3DXiTs8BITDskYUvXcCj.jpg","original_title":"おもひでぽろぽろ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":242828,"adult":false,"title":"When Marnie Was There","video":false,"overview":"Upon being sent to live with relatives in the countryside due to an illness, an emotionally distant adolescent girl becomes obsessed with an abandoned mansion and infatuated with a girl who lives there - a girl who may or may not be real.","genre_ids":[16,18,10751,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.0547,"vote_count":1921,"poster_path":"/vug1dvDI1tSa60Z8qjCuUE7ntkO.jpg","release_date":"2014-07-19","vote_average":7.937,"backdrop_path":"/rVDOeOccg0K9tXuw6b9uOG6q4mf.jpg","original_title":"思い出のマーニー","original_language":"ja"}],"similar_content":[{"id":589972,"adult":false,"title":"Little Vampire","video":false,"overview":"Little Vampire lives in a haunted house with a merry group of monsters, but he is bored stiff! One night, he secretly sneaks out of the manor along with his trusted bulldog, Phantomato, on a quest to find some new friends.","genre_ids":[16,10751,14],"popularity":0.3631,"vote_count":43,"poster_path":"/mLd9FVJTwnPO3ERv82ea5IZo6Hl.jpg","release_date":"2020-10-21","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/dAWrub4aTNMsh0pnYBiGPKZiREr.jpg","original_title":"Petit Vampire","original_language":"fr"},{"id":589973,"adult":false,"title":"SamSam","video":false,"overview":"SamSam, the smallest of the great heroes, has still not discovered his first superpower, while at home and at school, everyone has one! Faced with the worry of his parents and the mockery of his comrades, he goes in search of this hidden power. With the help of Mega, the new mysterious student of his school, Samsam embarks on this adventure full of cosmic monsters ...","genre_ids":[16,10751,878,12,35],"popularity":0.3545,"vote_count":14,"poster_path":"/nNMAglUfOuDuyAKYSmXzFkBeNha.jpg","release_date":"2020-02-05","vote_average":5.2,"backdrop_path":"/5T2kiBvi169qnCY8ul3btCRfJuf.jpg","original_title":"SamSam","original_language":"fr"},{"id":418956,"adult":false,"title":"The Ugly Duckling","video":false,"overview":"An outcast duckling's search for a family to accept him leads to constant rejection before learning his true identity as a swan.","genre_ids":[16,35],"popularity":0.9617,"vote_count":183,"poster_path":"/nCkMoq2penMxvdhQa0LGwK1G6fJ.jpg","release_date":"1939-04-07","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/woMB1t6cBbS9xPzZzsv8DI7IOxV.jpg","original_title":"The Ugly Duckling","original_language":"en"},{"id":647,"adult":false,"title":"Final Fantasy VII: Advent Children","video":false,"overview":"Two years have passed since the final battle with Sephiroth. Though Midgar, city of mako, city of prosperity, has been reduced to ruins, its people slowly but steadily walk the road to reconstruction. However, a mysterious illness called Geostigma torments them. With no cure in sight, it brings death to the afflicted, one after another, robbing the people of their fledgling hope.","genre_ids":[16,28,12,14,878],"popularity":2.093,"vote_count":1211,"poster_path":"/pTIXM2yu8McSlcQVs1VjVSNC45x.jpg","release_date":"2005-07-14","vote_average":7.161,"backdrop_path":"/8xhgpYyNSX5sJi0P35hwL73QYOV.jpg","original_title":"Final Fantasy VII: Advent Children","original_language":"ja"},{"id":673,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban","video":false,"overview":"Year three at Hogwarts means new fun and challenges as Harry learns the delicate art of approaching a Hippogriff, transforming shape-shifting Boggarts into hilarity and even turning back time. But the term also brings danger: soul-sucking Dementors hover over the school, an ally of the accursed He-Who-Cannot-Be-Named lurks within the castle walls, and fearsome wizard Sirius Black escapes Azkaban. And Harry will confront them all.","genre_ids":[12,14],"popularity":15.6854,"vote_count":22845,"poster_path":"/aWxwnYoe8p2d2fcxOqtvAtJ72Rw.jpg","release_date":"2004-05-31","vote_average":8.009,"backdrop_path":"/vbk5CfaAHOjQPSAcYm6AoRRz2Af.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban","original_language":"en"},{"id":756,"adult":false,"title":"Fantasia","video":false,"overview":"Walt Disney's timeless masterpiece is an extravaganza of sight and sound! See the music come to life, hear the pictures burst into song and experience the excitement that is Fantasia over and over again.","genre_ids":[16,10751,14],"popularity":4.2512,"vote_count":3268,"poster_path":"/5m9njnidjR0syG2gpVPVgcEMB2X.jpg","release_date":"1940-11-13","vote_average":7.342,"backdrop_path":"/lyzI5uFJC2E7sIYCCdaU0oZkDw2.jpg","original_title":"Fantasia","original_language":"en"},{"id":1294782,"adult":false,"title":"Spijtmoeders","video":false,"overview":"What if you love your child, but are unhappy in your role as a mother? Spijtmoeders is a documentary film about mothers who, if they could make the choice again, would rather not be mothers. Three women talk about their struggles with motherhood, the shame and guilt they feel, and the high expectations society places on them. The fear of judgment from others is great: what if people think that they are not a good mother, that they do not take good care of their child? What if they think they don't love their child? The mothers are represented by hyper-realistic dolls, but their voices are real.","genre_ids":[99,16],"popularity":0.1584,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/aBx5M9tMWL86WX69bcZvcv57jsl.jpg","release_date":"2024-05-16","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/5TcBArFvPlME0nINTEAu4uDcFop.jpg","original_title":"Spijtmoeders","original_language":"nl"},{"id":421594,"adult":false,"title":"Nana and Kaoru","video":false,"overview":"Kaoru is a 17-year-old boy with an SM fetish, secretly dreaming of an SM relationship with his childhood friend Nana. One day Kaoru's mother asks Nana to hide all his SM toys so that he will study for a change. However, Nana finds the leather one-piece that Kaoru bought and tries it on, but she accidentally locks it and does not have the key! This is the beginning of a very strange relationship...","genre_ids":[16,35],"popularity":0.7443,"vote_count":20,"poster_path":"/qCWi9MHrRctaCR82Rw3SZH20P2i.jpg","release_date":"2011-03-29","vote_average":4.8,"backdrop_path":"/u7rRtrJqngEFmptLsXQayC2cP4r.jpg","original_title":"ナナとカオル","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1997,"adult":false,"title":"Two Brothers","video":false,"overview":"Two tigers are separated as cubs and taken into captivity, only to be reunited years later as enemies by an explorer (Pearce) who inadvertently forces them to fight each other.","genre_ids":[12,18,10751],"popularity":1.3346,"vote_count":856,"poster_path":"/5I2pRuJI3SZVsxP5iaorGaczzkI.jpg","release_date":"2004-04-07","vote_average":7.077,"backdrop_path":"/aB5123I8MNi3NIg0t9RrP6A7Yla.jpg","original_title":"Deux Frères","original_language":"en"},{"id":2062,"adult":false,"title":"Ratatouille","video":false,"overview":"Remy, a resident of Paris, possesses a palate far more refined than that of his fellow comrades. He dreams of becoming a chef, determined to create culinary masterpieces rather than scavenge for scraps. There’s just one small problem: Remy is a rat. When fate deposits him in the sewers beneath one of Paris’s most famous restaurants, he finds himself ideally placed to fulfill his dream. Forming an unusual alliance with a bumbling young kitchen worker, Remy begins a daring culinary double life. Together, they must outwit the scheming Head Chef Skinner, evade Remy’s disapproving colony, and impress renowned food critic Anton Ego, who strikes fear in the hearts of chefs all throughout France.","genre_ids":[16,35,10751,14],"popularity":13.5564,"vote_count":18193,"poster_path":"/t3vaWRPSf6WjDSamIkKDs1iQWna.jpg","release_date":"2007-06-28","vote_average":7.836,"backdrop_path":"/xgDj56UWyeWQcxQ44f5A3RTWuSs.jpg","original_title":"Ratatouille","original_language":"en"},{"id":766423,"adult":false,"title":"Puparia","video":false,"overview":"Something is about to change drastically, and the only thing to do is to witness it.","genre_ids":[16,18,14],"popularity":0.1282,"vote_count":59,"poster_path":"/3KRpbwNDrQ8cqKoVknoPqqtrpAO.jpg","release_date":"2021-09-23","vote_average":7.958,"backdrop_path":"/6HRvFDiP894qvRLMu0nM0WeNbiC.jpg","original_title":"Puparia","original_language":"ja"},{"id":251519,"adult":false,"title":"Son of Batman","video":false,"overview":"Batman learns he has a violent, unruly pre-teen son, secretly raised by the terrorist group known as The League of Assassins.","genre_ids":[16,28,12],"popularity":1.6237,"vote_count":1127,"poster_path":"/yHx8OLSKc3VtIBB5lIe90c0fHOX.jpg","release_date":"2014-05-13","vote_average":7.066,"backdrop_path":"/jYqOnJDPI7QD9cGbE6CwDTp1tID.jpg","original_title":"Son of Batman","original_language":"en"},{"id":949394,"adult":false,"title":"Ensemble Stars!! -Road to Show--","video":false,"overview":"Ensemble Square - a brand new building in the middle of the city where countless people come and go. It’s home to four offices belonging to idols who spend their days singing and dancing. Films starring the Ensemble Square idols have been nominated for the Idol Film Festival (IFF), an annual festival held in New York City, and representative idols are selected to attend. The boys jet off to NYC to attend the festival and reception party, and afterward, head out on the town to see the sights and sounds. But a suspicious shadow is creeping up on them…","genre_ids":[16],"popularity":0.7096,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/hW4Y4Fy8khf4D3tlvwV82txg1uy.jpg","release_date":"2022-03-04","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/eTfbiJANxSTnrISIL9JSGeI8uur.jpg","original_title":"あんさんぶるスターズ！！-Road to Show!!-","original_language":"ja"},{"id":909,"adult":false,"title":"Meet Me in St. Louis","video":false,"overview":"A year in the life of a turn-of-the-century middle class family, leading up to the opening of the 1904 St. Louis World's Fair.","genre_ids":[35,18,10749,10751],"popularity":1.4702,"vote_count":422,"poster_path":"/ekVeUvG81pidsv2LMtWf5yYcNbq.jpg","release_date":"1944-11-28","vote_average":6.999,"backdrop_path":"/fQ93o3wVSIe0dXMLTVTBHoqWwew.jpg","original_title":"Meet Me in St. Louis","original_language":"en"},{"id":919,"adult":false,"title":"Blood: The Last Vampire","video":false,"overview":"In Japan, the vampire-hunter Saya, who is a powerful original, is sent by her liaison with the government, David, posed as a teenage student to the Yokota High School on the eve of Halloween to hunt down vampires. Saya asks David to give a new katana to her. Soon she saves the school nurse Makiho Amano from two vampires disguised of classmates and Makiho witnesses her fight against the powerful demon.","genre_ids":[16,14,27],"popularity":1.1511,"vote_count":362,"poster_path":"/uRwR5lcl55n5JSaTiYPwp5KjP6A.jpg","release_date":"2000-11-18","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/17s9ojb8j8QnBGCfqDUJraXLlFi.jpg","original_title":"BLOOD THE LAST VAMPIRE","original_language":"ja"},{"id":920,"adult":false,"title":"Cars","video":false,"overview":"Lightning McQueen, a hotshot rookie race car driven to succeed, discovers that life is about the journey, not the finish line, when he finds himself unexpectedly detoured in the sleepy Route 66 town of Radiator Springs. On route across the country to the big Piston Cup Championship in California to compete against two seasoned pros, McQueen gets to know the town's offbeat characters.","genre_ids":[16,12,35,10751],"popularity":9.3041,"vote_count":14884,"poster_path":"/2Touk3m5gzsqr1VsvxypdyHY5ci.jpg","release_date":"2006-06-08","vote_average":7.021,"backdrop_path":"/sd4xN5xi8tKRPrJOWwNiZEile7f.jpg","original_title":"Cars","original_language":"en"},{"id":953,"adult":false,"title":"Madagascar","video":false,"overview":"Four animal friends get a taste of the wild life when they break out of captivity at the Central Park Zoo and wash ashore on the island of Madagascar.","genre_ids":[10751,16,12,35],"popularity":8.9954,"vote_count":11528,"poster_path":"/zMpJY5CJKUufG9OTw0In4eAFqPX.jpg","release_date":"2005-05-25","vote_average":6.921,"backdrop_path":"/tPaurpIUskVji5vwV0dhy9pq4Vs.jpg","original_title":"Madagascar","original_language":"en"},{"id":1293708,"adult":false,"title":"AIKa: Special Trial","video":false,"overview":"An OVA released between episodes 5 and 6 of AIKa, that takes place between episodes 4 and 5.","genre_ids":[16,878,35],"popularity":0.2816,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/vLGtkrfmRqFh536eGmPpOUaLJiJ.jpg","release_date":"1998-05-25","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"AIKa Special TRIAL","original_language":"ja"},{"id":251733,"adult":false,"title":"The Brides of Sodom","video":false,"overview":"In a post apocalyptic world where vampires and witches rule, a male vampire falls in love with a human man, and wants to make him immortal.","genre_ids":[14,27,878],"popularity":0.1735,"vote_count":20,"poster_path":"/q7XNxsqiONJlFQNicLfpc3yrf98.jpg","release_date":"2013-01-28","vote_average":2.5,"backdrop_path":"/zZ6horsMHGnFk6cpma0KV8M7hr0.jpg","original_title":"The Brides of Sodom","original_language":"en"},{"id":251768,"adult":false,"title":"JLA Adventures: Trapped in Time","video":false,"overview":"Get ready for a battle of the ages when the Justice League faces off against its archenemies, the Legion of Doom, in an all-new movie from DC Comics. A mysterious being known as the Time Trapper arises, and a sinister plan led by Lex Luthor sends the Legion of Doom back in time to eliminate Superman, Wonder Woman and Batman before they become super heroes. For Aquaman, Flash and Cyborg, along with teen super heroes Karate Kid and Dawnstar, the stakes have never been higher, the rescue mission never deadlier. So join the fight for the future as the Justice League confronts its ultimate challenge… the threat of having never existed!","genre_ids":[10751,16,28,878],"popularity":0.7768,"vote_count":259,"poster_path":"/qchNuTbnleCtlIB8wyV03f36VuF.jpg","release_date":"2014-01-21","vote_average":6.645,"backdrop_path":"/mWzgMPlQcFZ6lZ449673LS2aCHX.jpg","original_title":"JLA Adventures: Trapped in Time","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt0096283","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q39571","instagram_id":null,"metacritic_id":"movie/my-neighbor-totoro","mydramalist_id":"14946","rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/my_neighbor_totoro"},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":110271,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki